<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">The following are some frequently asked questions about installing and using ITOM Container Deployment Foundation (CDF).</p><h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; background: none rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: 500; margin: 25px 0px 6px; overflow: hidden; padding-top: 0em; padding-bottom: 0.17em; border-bottom: none; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(0, 115, 231) !important; font-size: 24px !important;">What are the recommended deployment modes for CDF?</h2><ul style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.3em 0px 0px 1.6em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><li style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0.1em;">One master node, at least three worker nodes, and a separate NFS server.</li><li style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0.1em;">Multiple master nodes, at least three worker nodes, and a separate NFS server.</li></ul><h2><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 18.75pt 0in 4.5pt; line-height: 18.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><b><span style="font-size:18.0pt;font-family:&quot;MetricHPE_Medium&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;letter-spacing:.85pt">Can
I upgrade the suite images in CDF?<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 18.75pt 0in 4.5pt; line-height: 18.75pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">

